{"tid":1870571,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連登攬炒派又輸","createTime":"2020-02-09T02:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T03:15:50.000Z","uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"96ea994b6b57fa7f8c6d66162305c8af85ca5ee3","tid":1870571,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:40:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，講到武肺係威係勢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經傳有解藥了，攬炒又失敗"},{"pid":"75e38daa6af4ea9a6fdd295968a673b8941e7a5e","tid":1870571,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:40:47.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎「救命藥」主導者來自台灣】美供中國新藥卻被搶先註專利，意外挖出研發推手是台灣女科學家<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情蔓延全球，美國藥廠研發的「瑞德西韋」（Remdesivir）因治癒一例美國本土新型冠狀病毒患者，一天內症狀獲好轉且無副作用，美方因此免費提供給中國，但卻立刻被中國武漢病毒所搶先發表並申請專利。<br />\n<br />\n武漢研究所向外宣稱這是為了「保護國家利益」所為。隨著該款實驗性藥物受到關注，也才讓外界得知藥物主導者其實是來自台灣的女科學家楊台瑩（Taiyin Yang，音譯）博士。而目前我國政府也已與吉利德接洽，將有機會取得該藥物，供國內需要的患者使用。<br />\n<br />\n究竟研發武漢肺炎「救命藥」的台灣人來歷為何？一起來看。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/2020/02/07/remdesivir-wuhan-virus-medicine-from-taiwan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2F2020%2F02%2F07%2Fremdesivir-wuhan-virus-medicine-from-taiwan%2F&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=fb393c2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/2020/02/07/remdesivir-wuhan-virus-medicine-from-taiwan/</a>"},{"pid":"c4d8d21d51aa245c4f89e62ec0d09968048c26fa","tid":1870571,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:43:47.000Z","msg":"又話台灣好屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港豬仲笑唔笑台灣廢"},{"pid":"c62e0d9e95dcfb84376b1abc90df16871e3a1b51","tid":1870571,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c4d8d21d51aa245c4f89e62ec0d09968048c26fa","tid":1870571,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:43:47.000Z","msg":"又話台灣好屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港豬仲笑唔笑台灣廢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:45:09.000Z","msg":"留名恥笑攬炒派"},{"pid":"ae8f0009f05cc8aae554b5b8e81fa193fe58fde8","tid":1870571,"uid":127033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"太低裝 今日冇人工"}]}